\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4}{\ignorespaces Training trajectory analysis of Qwen3-0.6B-Base fine-tuned for 500 steps (11 checkpoints). (a)~Trajectory-PCA (MMSP Method A): checkpoints (colored by step) project onto a smooth curved arc in the top-2 PCA plane, overlaid on the loss surface contours. PC1+PC2 capture 87.6\% of trajectory variance. (b)~Training evolution: evaluation loss (left axis) shows rapid initial improvement then plateau; inter-checkpoint parameter distance (right axis) decreases monotonically, indicating convergence.}}{8}{figure.caption.8}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:trajectory}{{4}{8}{Training trajectory analysis of Qwen3-0.6B-Base fine-tuned for 500 steps (11 checkpoints). (a)~Trajectory-PCA (MMSP Method A): checkpoints (colored by step) project onto a smooth curved arc in the top-2 PCA plane, overlaid on the loss surface contours. PC1+PC2 capture 87.6\% of trajectory variance. (b)~Training evolution: evaluation loss (left axis) shows rapid initial improvement then plateau; inter-checkpoint parameter distance (right axis) decreases monotonically, indicating convergence}{figure.caption.8}{}}
